data.description: Welcome home to 218 Briar Hill Dr, a charming ranch-style residence where comfort meets timeless appeal! This 3 bed, 2 bathroom home features 1500 square feet of comfortable living space. You can't help but notice how well maintained this home has been as you walk through; a new roof (2023), newer siding, electrical updates just to name a few. Don't forget to check out the beautiful original hardwood floors throughout! The fully finished basement adds versatility to your living space, making it the perfect place to call home. Step into the backyard and enjoy the peaceful view of the woods and beautifully landscaped surroundings. The 12x16 custom-built shed, complete with electricity, provides ample storage space for all your needs. Welcome to your own oasis! Schedule your private showing
